by alexislefebvre at 2019-02-05T14:37:48Z

I don't know if `echo` and the Symfony console behaves in the same way but with `bash` in `gnome-terminal`, I have to use quote or escape the backslash in order to have the backslash in the output:

```
$ echo "App\Entity"
App\Entity
$ echo App\Entity
AppEntity
$ echo App\\Entity
App\Entity
```

