|               |   PHPStorm   |    cmder     |     cmd      |   git bash  | power shell |
|---------------|:------------:|:------------:|:------------:|:-----------:|:-----------:|
| 'App\Entity'  | 'App\Entity' | 'App\Entity' | 'App\Entity' | ok          | not tested  |
| "App\Entity"  | ok           | ok           | ok           | ok          | ok          |
| App\\\\Entity   | App\\\\Entity  | App\\\\Entity  | App\\\\Entity  | App\\\\Entity | not tested  |
| App\Entity    | ok           | ok           | ok           | AppEntity   | ok          |

